\sum_{n\in\mathbb Z}\delta(t-n)
b_n=2\int_{-1/2}^{1/2} \delta(t)\sin 2\pi n t\,dt = 2\sin (2\pi n \cdot 0) =0
a_n=2\int_{-1/2}^{1/2} \delta(t)\cos 2\pi n t\,dt = 2\cos (2\pi n \cdot 0) =2
1+2\sum_{n=1}^\infty \cos 2\pi n t \tag{1}
